    A hashable which knows how to transition from an absent hash state to a present hash state.

    A persisted store of hashes that can be used to compare previous builds of Steps to decide whether to rebuild.

    An ingredient that a Step can combine into an output.
    KeyedSerializable

    Plan
    A plan that executes steps by looking at which inputs have been satisfied.
    PlanKey
    A string wrapper for a key that refers to part of a plan.
    Step
    A step in the process of transforming inputs to outputs.
